  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749430/extras/177236d56abbe3e3861d8482d9f0bd3a.poster.avif?t=1718823490\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749430/extras/177236d56abbe3e3861d8482d9f0bd3a.webm?t=1718823490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749430/extras/177236d56abbe3e3861d8482d9f0bd3a.mp4?t=1718823490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create your own cozy cities while painting uncountable number of islands. Immerse yourself into a calming sandbox mode or go through 15 uncomplicated levels during which you will gradually understand all the gameplay features. The correct building placement will tend your city to grow. It is a colorful journey where you will find your own solutions for transition from one island to another.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749430/extras/ffcec856ba9194c16a93460055aa2de7.poster.avif?t=1718823490\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749430/extras/ffcec856ba9194c16a93460055aa2de7.webm?t=1718823490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749430/extras/ffcec856ba9194c16a93460055aa2de7.mp4?t=1718823490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
